message.entry: The crop rectangle does not intersect the image.
IMCROP expects a current figure containing an image.
No image found in the current axes.
IMCROP does not support 'XData' or 'YData' specified in [max,min] order.

The only syntaxes supported by IMCROP in code generation are:
 [...] = IMCROP(I,RECT)
 [...] = IMCROP(X,Y,I,RECT)
 [I2,RECT] = IMCROP(...)
 [X,Y,I2,RECT] = IMCROP(...)

The only syntaxes supported by IMCROP with categorical inputs are:
 [...] = IMCROP(I,RECT)
 [...] = IMCROP(X,Y,I,RECT)
 [I2,RECT] = IMCROP(...)
 [X,Y,I2,RECT] = IMCROP(...)
